update(int) - Method in class Fly
This method updates the fly's location in
the world
The fly can move in one of the four cardinal (N, S, E, W) directions.
You need to make sure that the updated location
is within the bounds of the world before
changing the location of the fly
update() - Method in class Frog
This method updates the frog's position.
It should randomly select one of the legal locations(if there any)
and set the frog's location to the chosen updated location.
